Interface ExperimentNode<T extends ExperimentType<S>,S>

      • process

        void process()
        Process this experiment node. The request will be passed down to the root experiment node and executed within the workspace. Only one experiment may be processed at a time for a workspace, and if an experiment is already in progress then invocation of this method should throw.

      • tryProcess

        boolean tryProcess()
        Attempt to process according to process(). If an experiment is already in progress then return false.
        Returns:
        true if the processing was able to start, false otherwise
